Visualization is split between Exploratory tools for the analyst and Presentation tools for external stakeholders.

Library	Customization Level	Primary Audience	Interactivity
Matplotlib	Total / Low-level	The Analyst (Internal)	Static
Seaborn	Medium / Statistical	The Analyst (Exploratory)	Static
Plotly/Dash	High	Stakeholders/Execs	Full (Web apps without JavaScript)

Automated EDA: YData Profiling

YData Profiling generates comprehensive reports in seconds. However, analysts must remain aware of its limitations:

1. Loss of Domain Nuance: It may miss domain-specific details that only a human expert can contextualize.
2. Performance Constraints: It can be extremely slow on datasets larger than 1 GB.
3. The Validation Requirement: Automated correlations are not causalities; they require manual validation of correlations to avoid misleading conclusions.

